					<ul>
						<li>Invitation hash sending from the room is fixed</li>
						<li>Invitation hash is now enable for plugin users</li>
						<li>First and last name can be passed to SOAP function for hash generation</li>
					</ul><br/>
					<br/>
					Other fixes<br/>
